ont color="#000000" face="Times"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt 13.5pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;"&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times" size="3"&gt;Pursuant to Title 36 CFR 261.50(e), the following are exempt from this restriction:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt 13.5pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;"&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in; text-indent: -22.5pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;"&gt;&lt;font face="Times"&gt;&lt;font size="3"&gt;&lt;font color="#000000"&gt;1. &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" size="3"&gt;Persons with a permit issued by a forest officer specifically authorizing the otherwise prohibited act or omission.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt 13.5pt; text-indent: -0.25in; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;"&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in; text-indent: -22.5pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;"&gt;&lt;font face="Times"&gt;&lt;font size="3"&gt;&lt;font color="#000000"&gt;2. &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" size="3"&gt;Any Federal, State, or local officer, or member of an organized rescue or fire fighting force in the performance of an official duty.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;"&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&